{"tid":161244,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"17 個《求婚大作戰》經典回顧！網友說：神日劇誰來拍都無法超越","createTime":"2017-03-18T11:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T16:11:49.000Z","uid":9573,"like":155,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"188236a31e8299479476addbfe1054e0b5a2fe1e","tid":161244,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c7971d9e12c.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c7971d9e12c.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=460fe4a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《 求婚大作戰 》是不少人心目中最經典的日劇，即是已是十年前的劇，仍然經得起時間的考驗，重看多少次仍覺得相當精彩。繼韓國於 2012 年翻拍後，中國版也於上個月完成了拍攝。不少人知道這個消息後，紛紛大叫「不要破壞我的美好回憶！」山下智久與長澤雅美已演繹了在我們心中無可取替的版本。你把這套劇重看了多少遍？讓我們一起來回顧一下吧！<br />\n<br />\n經典回顧：<br />\n<br />\n《求婚大作戰》講述一對青梅竹馬的好友，岩瀨健及吉田禮。兩人心裡一直喜歡對方，卻不斷錯過對方。終於，禮要和大學教授多田哲也結婚了。在婚禮中，健一直看著充滿回憶的幻燈片，不斷後悔過去多年沒有向禮表白。此時，教堂精靈深受感動而出現，他擁有控制時間的能力，讓健可以回到幻燈片中的時間，改變與禮的未來。<br />\n<br />\n1. 「哈利路亞，Chance！」<br />\n「哈利路亞，Chance！」這句經典的對白令健可以回到過去，向禮表達心意。每次聽到這句對白，都會覺得很有衝勁，健必定要成功啊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c7993e24d3e.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c7993e24d3e.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=c6456b8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 黑板上的祝福<br />\n<br />\n禮、繪理、幹雄、小鶴故意令健受到老師的懲罰，然後偷偷在黑板上畫下滿滿的生日祝福，這完全是中學回憶啊！相信大家在學生時期都做過這類驚喜吧！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c7994c12a78.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c7994c12a78.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=a02fc46b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 圖書館裡的秘密<br />\n六年前，健並沒有發現禮留給他的生日禮物。這次回到過去，健終於發現了這個模型。兩人的關係一步一步接近。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c79953a527e.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c79953a527e.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=2429ce98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 錯過了的告白<br />\n<br />\n健第一次表露心跡，離開學校之前在黑板上寫上表白字句「最重要的人，就坐在我身旁。」然後叮囑禮明天要早一點回校。結果，實習老師早一步將表白字句擦掉了，而這人更是禮將來的結婚對象－－多田老師！是天大的諷刺啊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c7995aedf15.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c7995aedf15.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=33d6854b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 「岩瀨健三」<br />\n「岩瀨健三」，是禮對健獨一無二的綽號。因為小學時借用橡皮擦的一個舉動，成為了健和禮結緣的原因。「岩瀨健三年G組」的橡皮擦折成一半後，巧合地成了「岩瀨健三」。相信每個人也試過，對暗戀或曖昧的人起一個專屬自己的綽號，只有兩人才明白其意思的綽號。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c7996293392.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c7996293392.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=3dc8d0a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c7996a2fcc1.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c7996a2fcc1.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=72f7ade9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 最特別的第二顆鈕釦<br />\n「第二顆鈕釦」是日本一個特別的傳統，女方會在畢業典禮那天向男生索取校服上的第二顆鈕釦。如果男生交出鈕釦，代表男生同樣也有愛慕之意。為甚麼一定是第二顆鈕釦？因為這顆鈕釦最接近心臟，代表著男生整個中學歲月。可是，誤會之下，健失去了校服的第二顆鈕釦。最終，健把棒球制服上的第二顆鈕釦送給禮，「這件經你手、充滿著你的真心的棒球制服，才是我高中時代的象徵。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c7997383689.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c7997383689.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=2a4d1463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 「總說明天才做的人是傻瓜！」<br />\n第五集是筆者最愛的一集，禮的爺爺從鄉下來到東京找禮，可愛活潑的爺爺說出了很多金句，「以為不用說出口對方也會懂是大錯特錯！」「總說明天才做的人是傻瓜！」句句也發人深省，雖然是顯淺易明的道理，但不是人人也能夠做到。這次回到過去，健想起了爺爺這次之後就沒有再去東京找禮，因為爺爺後來已去世了。因此提醒禮要把握機會找爺爺訴說心底話。無論重看多少次，這集還是賺了筆者許多眼淚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c7997e5bfa4.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c7997e5bfa4.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=88945f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c799873d563.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c799873d563.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=fc842b07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8. 真正的初吻<br />\n禮埋怨健忘記了他倆的「初吻」，在小學運動會中，兩人因為二人三足跌成一團，在混亂之中親到的。健說：「那種不算初吻啊。」然後拉著禮，一下子就親上去了！這是筆者看得最激動的時刻啊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c7999272954.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c7999272954.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=be8495ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c79999cf43e.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c79999cf43e.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=99af3c61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f3e1b5385d21968707c63b024ec9891eb7c6f19","tid":161244,"uid":9573,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:59:34.000Z","msg":"9. 二十歲前的了斷<br />\n兩人真真正正走上分岔路，是第六集。原來禮早在中學三年級已經寫了一封告白信給健，卻遲遲沒有送出信，一直覺得放在身上，總會有個時機可以交給健。可是到了十九歲的最後一天，信仍未有送出。禮決定要在二十歲前把一切搞清楚。卻因為雙方的很多「自以為」錯過了對方，禮因為找不到「答案」，決定要放下健了，與多田老師的關係也更進一步。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c799a94120e.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c799a94120e.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=57d1749d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c799b02eb90.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c799b02eb90.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=7529f1cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10. 勇敢的告白<br />\n很多劇集裡的第二男主角都會很討人厭，但多田老師完全與討厭拉不上關係。多田老師的溫柔、勇敢，喜歡禮就直說的態度，很令人敬佩。多田老師藉著「國王遊戲」在眾人面前向禮告白，做了健這麼多年不敢做的事。筆者一方面會替健感到著急，但另一方面卻打從心底裡喜歡多田老師。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c799bc79b9b.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c799bc79b9b.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=273eaa19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c799c379ba5.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c799c379ba5.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=a3889655&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n11. 第一次改變未來<br />\n這是劇中第一個改變未來的驚喜位！在健的鼓勵之下，小鶴勇敢地叫繪理不要再當前度隨傳隨到的玩偶，此舉竟然改變了未來，當健回到婚禮中，發現小鶴與繪理成為了戀人！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c799cd6654c.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c799cd6654c.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=043eedb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12. 「有誰不在這裡也會變成理所當然嗎？」<br />\n因為多次回到過去都無法改變禮與多田結婚的結局，健決定要回到過去遺忘禮。大伙兒準備一起到海邊看日出迎接新年，健卻離開了大伙兒。眾人到了海邊後，才感到沒有了健，甚麼也沒有了意義。一個圈子裡缺少了誰，感覺亦再也不一樣。「有誰不在這裡也會變成理所當然嗎？」這又是一大共鳴位。中學畢業後，好友們還能夠一個不少的聚在一起嗎？這套劇除了述說愛情，描繪健、禮、繪理、幹雄、小鶴五人的友情也相當動人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c799d519b37.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c799d519b37.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=29db20e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n13. 「和我結婚吧。」<br />\n花了這麼多時間，健還是沒有把心意說出口。禮準備要答應多田老師的求婚了，健終於上前擁著禮，叫禮與自己結婚。可是，這個舉動已經挽回不了甚麼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c799dcec31e.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c799dcec31e.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=f88055f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n14. 畢業後仍能不變的友誼？<br />\n「大學畢業後，五人就很少聚在一起。但無論多久沒見，一間就像重回學生時代。」你又有沒有這樣的好友，無論多久沒見，一見面就能夠盡興的聚在一起？<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c799e3bf70d.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c799e3bf70d.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=bb1b1dfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c799eb8f1ca.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c799eb8f1ca.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=f0f55c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n15. 有過去才有今天的你<br />\n在禮和多田老師仍未交往的時候，禮曾經因為健而在多田面前哭了。禮在他們快要結婚的時候，問多田為甚麼從來不問那時候哭的原因。「因為有我所不知道的你，才有現在的你。包括有那些過去的你，我全部都喜歡。」有多少人能夠像多田老師一樣，不計較愛人的過去？因為有過去的傷心難過，才會成就了今天的你。過去每個錯失、難過都有意義。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c799f7c34ad.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c799f7c34ad.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=d07990fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c79a011385a.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c79a011385a.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=44c527aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/69z1R5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69z1R5.png&h=320f4a3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n16. 婚禮上的告白<br />\n<br />\n「我，喜歡過禮，說實話，現在也喜歡著禮。」「禮，恭喜你結婚，請你幸福。不幸福的話，我是不會原諒你的。」健沒有在「過去」改變禮與多田結婚的結局，反而是因為「現在」的致辭令禮回心轉意。筆者很喜歡這一點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c79a37d5169.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c79a37d5169.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=16ec607d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c79a2b6451c.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c79a2b6451c.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=80face62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n17. SP中的完滿結局<br />\n在《求婚大作戰SP》中，禮和健一直避談「結婚」這個話題，健令禮悔婚，這個話題始終比較尷尬。健因為要幫助小鶴與繪理順利結婚，再一次回到過去，亦藉此面對他與禮不敢面對的問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c79a58d186d.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c79a58d186d.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=7fc1e534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「雖然將來我們可能會吵架，也會彼此發很多牢騷，也會有懶得聽對方說話的時候，但我仍然想要你陪在我身邊。我會一輩子照顧你。」禮接受了健的求婚，為這套神劇畫上了完滿的句號。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63655/58c79a6046dde.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63655%2F58c79a6046dde.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=5312e409&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f932b224b54ea2fdc7f8685afa2e0129771d407","tid":161244,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:09:58.000Z","msg":"好撚期待大陸版呀！"},{"pid":"087c89f9b5f9abb10147c847fa6a2451a09a79fd","tid":161244,"uid":11311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12b1aee31d081a86ad9f3b6afe8d5bcedf25006","tid":161244,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:18:19.000Z","msg":"屌你無啦啦有張朱千雪 搞到我諗左十秒求婚邊有依一幕呀<br />\n條女邊撚個來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重睇過五次求婚 蝗國同垃圾韓去食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41d7f1a704750214b80265e66430631d9339a62","tid":161244,"uid":40818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:23:48.000Z","msg":"祈禱吧，否則不會讓你如願；<br />\n尋找吧，否則不會讓你發現；<br />\n敲門吧，否則不會為你敞開。"},{"pid":"f81be0dcd1ab929729799efc5fcd9eef2bbd2530","tid":161244,"uid":58161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:26:21.000Z","msg":"我個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入呢個PO之前又睇左一次 百看不厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d684cbec7149575be36c899f88321cdae4a175a1","tid":161244,"uid":2040,"like":1,"dislike